init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a secret group called the "C-Team" and no one knows about them except for the former presidents and those they protect.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The helicopter landed in my back yard, and two heavily armed SAS troopers escorted me to the chopper.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I got out of the helicopter, and another soldier gave me a headset that would translate any alien languages I ran into.

actions.text: JFK smiled and said "Let's get started."
